headline: UBS Raises Amgen (AMGN) Target as Pharma and Biotech Setup Improves
summary: Amgen Inc. (NASDAQ:AMGN) is included among the 12 Best Dow Jones Dividend Stocks to Buy According to Hedge Funds. On January 26, UBS lifted its price target on Amgen Inc. (NASDAQ:AMGN) to $390 from $380 and kept a Buy rating on the stock. The call reflects a more constructive view on the broader US pharma […]
